<div n="1"><head>EXTENT AND POPULATION OF AMERICA.</head><lb/><p>The following estimate of the extent, in square leagues and<lb/>population, of the continent of America in 1822 was lately<lb/>transmitted by Baron de Humboldt from Paris, to President<lb/>Bolivar, with the accompanying letter:&#x2014;</p>
    
    <lb break="yes"/>
    <lb break="yes"/>
    <table>
        <row>
            <cell/>
            <cell> Square Leagues.</cell>
            <cell> Population.</cell>
        </row>
        <lb break="yes"/>
        <row>
            <cell>Mexico, or New Spain</cell>
            <cell>75,830</cell>
            <cell>6,800,000</cell>
        </row>
        <lb break="yes"/>
        <row>
            <cell>Guatemala</cell>
            <cell>16,740</cell>
            <cell>1,600,000</cell>
        </row>
        <lb break="yes"/>
        <row>
            <cell>Cuba and Puerto Rico</cell>
            <cell>4,430</cell>
            <cell>800,000</cell>
        </row>
        <lb break="yes"/>
        <row>
            <cell rows="3">Colombia <list rendition="#leftBraced">
                <item>Venezuela</item>
                <item>New Granada</item>
            </list></cell>
        </row>
        <row>
            <cell>33,700</cell>
            <cell>900,000</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
            <cell>58,250</cell>
            <cell>1,800,000</cell>
        </row>
        <row/>
        <row>
            <cell>Peru</cell>
            <cell>42,150</cell>
            <cell>1,400,000</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
            <cell>Chili</cell>
            <cell>14,240</cell>
            <cell>1,100,000</cell>
        </row>
        <lb break="yes"/>
        <row>
            <cell>Buenos Ayres</cell>
            <cell>126,770</cell>
            <cell>2,000,000</cell>
        </row>
        <lb break="yes"/>
        <row>
            <cell/>
            <cell>_____________</cell>
            <cell>_____________</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
            <cell>Total formerly Spanish</cell>
            <cell>372,110</cell>
            <cell>16,400,000</cell>
        </row>
        <lb break="yes"/>
        <row>
            <cell>   United States</cell>
            <cell>125,440</cell>
